  <brief_title>Efficacy/Safety of Cilnidipine Plus Valsartan Versus Valsartan in Patients With Hypertension</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of the Efficacy and Safety of Cilnidipine 10mg/Valsartan 160mg Combination Therapy, Cilnidipine 5mg/Valsartan 160mg Combination Therapy and Valsartan 160mg Monotherapy in Hypertensive Patients Inadequately Controlled With Valsartan 160mg Monotherapy: a Multicenter, Randomized, Double Blind Phase III Study</official_title>
